    "description": "CUET Micro-Ops Hackathon 2025 - Premer Prantor UIU\n\nThis collection contains all API endpoints for the Delineate file download service.\n\n## Base URL\n- Local: http://localhost:3000\n\n## Challenge 2: Long-Running Download Architecture\nThis API demonstrates handling long-running downloads with variable processing times (5-15s in dev, 10-120s in production).",
